 href=\"https://rgbcmyk.com.ar/en/xla-2/\">Excel </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brucelindbloom.com/index.html?Math.html\">Formula</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brucelindbloom.com/index.html?ColorCalculator.html\">Color Calculator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.unitpedia.com/color-converter/\">Unitpedia</a> HEX, RGB, HSL, CMYK, HSV, Lab, Lch, Xyz, Hwb</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.colorhexa.com/\">Colorhexa</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://colors.acutecomponents.com/\">Acute Components</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://coolors.co/bd3848\">Coolors</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"note-on-lch-to-rgb-conversion\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#note-on-lch-to-rgb-conversion\" aria-label=\"note on lch to rgb conversion permalink\" class=\"toc-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Note on LCH to RGB Conversion</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://convertingcolors.com/\">Converting Color</a>, clamping if outside RGB gamut</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.unitpedia.com/color-converter/\">Unitpedia</a>, clamping if outside RGB gamut</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://colormine.org/color-converter\">Colormine</a>, clamping if outside RGB gamut</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://css.land/lch/\">CSS Land</a>, clamping if outside RGB gamut (but inform the clamping)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.easyrgb.com/en/convert.php\">Easy RGB</a>, not clamping</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brucelindbloom.com/index.html?ColorCalculator.html\">Bruce Lind Bloom</a>, not clamping</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.colorhexa.com/